bd5a8\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://justreal.me/petition/photo.html</a><br />\n<br />\n(8）德國減少對中國和其他非民主國家的依賴 30.12.2019<br />\n<a href=\"https://epetitionen.bundestag.de/petitionen/_2019/_09/_01/Petition_98731.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fepetitionen.bundestag.de%2Fpetitionen%2F_2019%2F_09%2F_01%2FPetition_98731.html&d=CRZj9ITMXIzKHLmvffUzPJS3ibws79Cb3MvuL7akqOg%3D&h=0731aa3b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://epetitionen.bundestag.de/petitionen/_2019/_09/_01/Petition_98731.html</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n重有，我認為宜家下下靠名人呼籲D人聯署唔太可行，所以我有一個諗法，如果可以設計一個網站，集合所有外國聯署，再教人點聯署，係咪可行？<br />\n<br />\n真心歡迎討論，求幫手推"},{"pid":"1dc46f76ab788e0e244687f4c331435a95020d10","tid":1800083,"uid":114792,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-27T13:57:51.000Z","msg":"(Non IT)<br />\n有冇印象以前ig 有嗰啲叫做30 days challenges<br />\n有啲係一日喺ig分享一首歌 做足30日<br />\n<br />\n會唔會可以搵一啲出名啲嘅文宣ig<br />\n每日派任務 做完就ig po story <br />\n有聯署就簽聯署<br />\n冇聯署可以係其他一啲好簡單嘅野"},{"pid":"955bfa7956d46118feaaf493a4c2c042fcbe8809","tid":1800083,"uid":246588,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-27T15:08:31.000Z","msg":"我真心覺得要set up個網站，有無IT手足比idea"},{"pid":"8d7128a9223ca9249818562a8090e3cd455fffb0","tid":1800083,"uid":8423,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-27T16:33:12.000Z","msg":"有冇 tg channel ？<br />\n我記得有"},{"pid":"2a7021315b1b5b6a42e80b37cc85a7237add1284","tid":1800083,"uid":8423,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-27T16:34:07.000Z","msg":"德國人權法全球馬格尼茨基法案<br />\n要快<br />\n唔夠人<br />\n人地再三請求啦已經"},{"pid":"70a66424e621b7cbd6bbc1c8e01f7033841765ea","tid":1800083,"uid":246588,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8d7128a9223ca9249818562a8090e3cd455fffb0","tid":1800083,"uid":8423,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-27T16:33:12.000Z","msg":"有冇 tg channel ？<br />\n我記得有"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-27T18:12:57.000Z","msg":"呢個？淨係白宮喎<br />\n<br /